ct Code","sections":{"manufacturerInfo":"Manufacturer Details","importerInfo":"Importer Details","packerInfo":"Packer Details","countryOfOrigin":"Country of Origin"}},"maskedSellerPopup":{"heading":"More Information","subHeading":"Product Code","sections":{"importerInfo":"Importer Details","countryOfOrigin":"Country of Origin"}},"testing":{"remove":"this"}},"checkout.addToCartMessaging":{"itemAlreadyPresent":"You have this item in your bag and we have increased the quantity by 1","itemReachedMaxQty":"You have this item in your bag with the maximum available quantity","itemAlreadyPresentAsFreeGift":"Item can't be added to cart, already present as free gift"},"web.skinAnalyser":{"disclaimer":"You are now migrating to a third party platform (\"Revieve Platform\") owned and operated by Revieve Oy (\"Revieve\") to use and experience the \"AI Skin Care Analyzer''. By proceeding further you agree to be bound by the terms and conditions of Revieve and to \u003ca href='https://www.myntra.com/skin-analyser/terms-and-conditions'>these terms\u003c/a>. \u003cbr />You expressly declare that you are 18 years old or above. Myntra has no ownership or control whatsoever in the analysis, advice or recommendations provided on the Revieve Platform. If you use ‘AI Skin Care Analyzer’ or specifically grant permission to Revieve, or otherwise provide any consent on the Revieve Platform, you may be required to share your information with Revieve. The processing and usage of such information shall be subject to Revieve's terms of use and privacy policy and Myntra shall not be liable or responsible in any manner whatsoever.\u003cbr />The ‘AI Skin Care Analyzer’ solution is provided by Revieve solely for your convenience to analyse your skin concerns using artificial intelligence technology and provide skincare product recommendations based on the same. It does not constitute and in no case is intended to be a substitute to medical or other professional advice.\u003cbr />","button":"PROCEED","waitMessage":"Please wait, loading...","ref_id":"SKIN_ANALYSER","terms":{"header":"Terms and Conditions","items":["This feature \u003cspan class='bold'>(“AI Skin Care Analyzer”)\u003c/span> is a feature to analyse skin concerns and recommend skincare products using Artificial Intelligence technology and is available on the subpage \u003cspan class='bold'>(“Revieve Platform”)\u003c/span> which is owned and operated by Revieve Oy, Helsinki Finland, a third-party entity \u003cspan class='bold'>(“Revieve”)\u003cspan>.","Revieve Platform is being hosted and made available to users \u003cspan class='bold'>(“Users/You”)\u003c/span> on Myntra mobile application \u003cspan class='bold'>(“Myntra Platform”)\u003c/span>. The Myntra Platform is owned and operated by Myntra Designs Private Limited \u003cspan class='bold'>(“Myntra”, “We” or “Our”)\u003c/span>.","By clicking on this page or using any service or features, You agree and acknowledge to being redirected to Revieve Platform and Revieve will collect and  process it and use it according to their privacy policy. Please visit \u003ca href='https://www.myntra.com/privacypolicy'>Privacy policy\u003c/a>.  If you do not agree to these T&Cs, please do not access or use this AI Skin Care Analyzer feature.","Myntra is only hosting the Revieve Platform within the Myntra Platform, and as such, Myntra has no control in the analysis, advice or recommendations rendered on the Revieve Platform.","By hosting the Revieve Platform, Myntra is not engaging in the business of rendering any analysis or advice or recommendations listed on the Revieve Platform; Myntra is merely making the Revieve Platform discoverable on the Myntra Platform for its customers and enabling its customers to browse and use the AI Skin Care Analyzer feature on the Revieve Platform, based on the terms and subject to the conditions mentioned therein.","By hosting the Revieve Platform, Myntra is neither guaranteeing nor giving any warranty nor making any representation with respect to the accuracy of the analysis, advice or recommendations provided on the Revieve Platform. Further, Myntra does not review, monitor, approve, endorse or interfere with respect to processing and usage of the information provided by You to Revieve and Myntra shall not be held liable for any breach in this regard. The processing and usage of such information shall be under the control of Revieve.","Myntra is neither endorsing Revieve, the analysis, advice or recommendations offered on the Revieve Platform or the Revieve Platform by itself, and disclaims all liability and responsibility, whatsoever, for the quality, availability merchantability, features and/or content listed, offered or rendered on the Revieve Platform.","Any information on the Revieve Platform, whether the content, analysis, recommendations or any other information, have not been verified, reviewed or approved by Myntra, therefore, Myntra shall not be responsible for any such content, analysis or recommendations or information or accuracy or quality of the products sold/displayed by Revieve. Myntra will not undertake any obligation or bear any liability with respect to the accuracy of the AI Skin Care Analyzer used by You on the Revieve Platform.","We may store the analysis, advice or recommendations provided by Revieve. We use this information to do research on our users' demographics, interests, and behaviour to better understand, protect and serve our users. This information is compiled and analysed on an aggregated basis. Please read our \u003ca href='https://www.myntra.com/privacypolicy'>Privacy policy\u003c/a>  on how we use and process this information.","If You choose to purchase any product recommended on the Revieve Platform, You will be redirected to Myntra Platform for making payments, and completing your purchase. You acknowledge and agree that, in this case, Myntra’s role is limited to enabling your purchase on the Myntra Platform. Myntra will neither be a party to nor in any manner concerned with the analysis, advice or recommendation rendered on Revieve Platform nor be liable or responsible for any act or omission on Your part or on part of Revieve.","Myntra has no control on the analysis, advice or recommendation offered to You on the Revieve Platform. Therefore, We will not be in a position to address any queries raised by You with respect to Your browsing of the Revieve Platform or use of the AI Skin Care Analyzer.  Revieve shall be liable for redressing all queries and complaints; and You can directly contact Revieve for the same.","We do not represent that access to the Revieve Platform will be uninterrupted, error free, free of viruses or other harmful components or that such defects will be corrected. We do not warrant that the Revieve Platform will be compatible with all hardware and software which You may use.","For the purpose of using the AI Skin Care Analyzer, Revieve may request access to your camera and/or gallery to take a selfie or image, and You may be required to give your consent to use your camera or folder from your mobile device. Any images captured is in control of Revieve and Myntra shall not have access to such images.","Myntra does not encourage the ‘AI Skin Care Analyzer’ feature for use by persons under the age of 18 years. If You are under 18 years old, You should not use the 'AI Skin Care Analyzer' feature or provide Revieve with any personally identifiable information.","If You do not want to provide your images, you may try other features available on Revieve Platform such as ‘Pick matching conditions’ under the “AI Skin Care Analyzer” feature in the Revieve Platform.","The “AI Skin Care Analyzer” feature is provided solely for the User’s convenience to analyse the User’s skin concerns and provide skincare product recommendations based on the same and does not constitute any medical or professional advice or expertise.","The information provided on the Revieve Platform is for general information purposes and use only and the AI Skin Care Analyzer feature is provided solely for the User’s convenience to analyse the User’s skin concerns and provide skincare product recommendations based on the same but in no case is it intended to be a substitute for medical or other professional advice. The User is responsible for ensuring the product they purchase is suitable for their specific requirements and Myntra shall not be held responsible for any product purchased by the User based on the “AI Skin Care Analyzer'' feature. ","The “AI Skin Care Analyzer” feature is to be used as a guide. User agrees and acknowledges that there is no guarantee with respect to the accuracy, adequacy or results of use of the respective products and their suitability and actual results may vary. Myntra will not be responsible for any choice made by the User to make a purchase of a skincare product.","NOTWITHSTANDING ANYTHING TO THE CONTRARY HEREIN, THE AI SKIN CARE ANALYZER FEATURE IS MADE AVAILABLE ON THE REVIEW PLATFORM THROUGH MYNTRA “AS IS” AND MYNTRA HEREBY EXPRESSLY DISCLAIMS ALL REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED, REGARDING THE FEATURE OR ANY PORTION THEREOF, INCLUDING ANY IMPLIED WARRANTY OF MERCHANTABILITY OR FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE AND IMPLIED WARRANTIES ARISING FROM COURSE OF DEALING OR COURSE OF PERFORMANCE. MYNTRA GIVES NO WARRANTY OR UNDERTAKING IN RELATION TO THE DISPLAY OF PRODUCTS OR OTHER INFORMATION, INCLUDING IN RELATION TO THE AI SKIN CARE ANALYZER FEATURE. MYNTRA DOES NOT WARRANT THAT THE FUNCTIONS CONTAINED IN THE “AI SKIN CARE ANALYZER” FEATURE WILL MEET USER’S REQUIREMENTS, OR THAT THE FEATURE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, ACHIEVE ANY INTENDED RESULT, MEET ANY PERFORMANCE OR RELIABILITY STANDARDS, OR BE ERROR FREE, OR THAT ANY ERRORS OR DEFECTS CAN OR WILL BE CORRECTED.","Myntra reserves the right at its sole discretion, to terminate, withdraw, suspend, amend, extend, modify, add or remove the Revieve Platform and “AI Skin Care Analyzer” feature, at any time without any prior written notice.","You acknowledge and confirm that You are aware of the nature of telecommunications/ internet services and that an email transmission may not be received properly and may be read or be known to any unauthorised persons. You agree to assume and bear all the risks involved in respect of such errors and misunderstanding and Myntra shall not be responsible in any manner.","You are not bound in any way to use the “AI Skin Care Analyzer” feature. Any action towards using the “AI Skin Care Analyzer” feature is voluntary.","You hereby agree to indemnify and keep Myntra harmless against all damages, liabilities, costs, expenses, claims, suits and proceedings (including reasonable attorney's fee) that may be suffered by Myntra as a consequence of (i) violation of terms of these Terms and Conditions by You; (ii) violation of applicable laws; (iii) any action or inaction resulting in wilful misconduct or negligence on Your part.","In case of any dispute or difference arising concerning these terms and conditions, the same shall be under the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Bangalore, Karnataka.","This document is an electronic record in terms of Information Technology Act, 2000, and the Rules there under as applicable and the amended provisions pertaining to electronic records in various statutes as amended by the Information Technology Act, 2000. This electronic record is generated by a computer system and does not require any physical or digital signatures."]}},"web.modiface":{"title":"Terms and Conditions","items":["By accessing the Try On feature or providing your information, you expressly agree to be bound by these terms and conditions and our \u003ca href='https://www.myntra.com/privacypolicy'>Privacy Policy\u003c/a>","The \u003cspan class='bold'>‘Live Try On’\u003c/span> or \u003cspan class='bold'>‘Upload a Selfie’\u003c/span> feature is not intended for use by persons under the age of 18 years. If you are under 18 years old, you should not use the Try-On feature or provide us with any personally identifiable information. If you disclose any personal information relating to other people to us, you represent that you have the authority to do so and to permit us to use the information in accordance with these terms and conditions and our \u003ca href='https://www.myntra.com/privacypolicy'>Privacy Policy\u003c/a>.","We may track your buying behavior, preferences, and other information that you choose to provide on our Platform. We use this information to do internal research on the feature, demographics, interests, and behavior to better understand, protect and serve our users. This information is compiled and analyzed on an aggregated basis. This information may be shared with our third-party agents for analysis and for enhancing your try-on experience. To know more on how we process your personal information, please see our \u003ca href='https://www.myntra.com/privacypolicy'>Privacy Policy\u003c/a>."]},"rnw.appData":{"version":"4.2106.0","updatedVersion":"4.2401.20","appVersion":"4.2506.10","pdpRnwEnabled":true,"plpRnwEnabled":true,"pdpSSREnabled":false,"pdpSSREnabledNew":true,"plpSSREnabled":true,"leDBSize":5,"leDBEnabled":true,"plpSSRDebug":{"htmlDisabled":false,"ssrSupportedwidgets":["IMAGE_SWIPE","ADD_BUTTONS","PDP_PRODUCT_INFO","SIZE_SELECTOR","EARLY_BIRD_OFFER","MINI_PRODUCT_BANNER","DISCLAIMERS","NEP","EMI_V2","STYLE_TRENDS","EXPIRY_INFO","BOTTOM_VIEW_INFO","COLOUR_SELECTOR","PILLS_FILTER","CAROUSEL_BANNER","LOCATION_STRIP","BOTTOM_FILTER","DYNAMIC_BANNER"]},"rnwSupported":{"chrome":{"blink":65,"webkit":605},"chrome webview":65,"mobile safari":12,"webkit":605,"samsung browser":10,"samsung internet":10,"firefox":{"gecko":65,"webkit":605},"miui browser":{"blink":70,"webkit":605},"android browser":{"blink":70,"webkit":605},"opera":{"blink":70,"webkit":605},"ucbrowser":{"blink":70,"webkit":605},"instagram":{"blink":65,"webkit":605},"facebook":{"blink":65,"webkit":605,"ios":12},